recent_articles.title: Tempus AI rebound, Meta's AI ad push, Broadcom earnings optimism
recent_articles.summary:
Market Domination co-host Julie Hyman tracks today's top moving stocks and biggest market stories in this Market Minute.

Tempus AI (TEM) shares jump after TD Cowen responded to a recent short report, calling some of its claims exaggerated.

Advertising stocks fall as Meta (META) reportedly plans to fully automate ad creation and targeting with artificial intelligence (AI) by the end of next year, according to The Wall Street Journal.

Meanwhile, Broadcom (AVGO) shares rise ahead of its June 5 earnings report.

Stay up to date on the latest market action, minute-by-minute, with Yahoo Finance's Market Minute.
